word_group.brief_definition: 在网上；在互联网上；在因特网上

bilingual.source: He uses the Internet and talks to friends.
bilingual.target: 他使用互联网并与朋友聊天。

bilingual.source: These videos are uploaded onto the Internet.
bilingual.target: 这些视频被上传到互联网上。

bilingual.source: The Internet brings the world of English to you.
bilingual.target: 互联网将英语世界带给你。

bilingual.source: Social communication taken over by the Internet.
bilingual.target: 社交交流被互联网接管了。

bilingual.source: Grandma and I had a nice chat about the Internet.
bilingual.target: 我和奶奶聊了一下互联网。

bilingual.source: How can you use the Internet to learn English?
bilingual.target: 你如何利用互联网学习英语？

bilingual.source: Will people do all things on the internet?
bilingual.target: 人们会在互联网上做所有事情吗？

bilingual.source: The Internet has greatly improved Jan's life.
bilingual.target: 互联网极大地改善了简的生活。

list.abstract: 互联网（internet），又称国际网络，是指网络与网络之间所串连成的庞大网络，这些网络以一组通用的协议相连，形成逻辑上的单一巨大国际网络，开始于1969年。 它与万维网（WWW）不同，其可以提供广泛的信息资源、点对点网络、文件共享以及IP电话服务等。 2024年3月22日，中国互联网络信息中心发布第53次《中国互联网络发展状况统计报告》。《报告》显示，截至2023年12月，中国网民规模达10.92亿人，较2022年12月新增网民2480万人，互联网普及率达77.5%。
Internet，中文正式译名为因特网，又叫做国际互联网。它是由那些使用公用语言互相通信的计算机连接而成的全球网络。一旦你连接到它的任何一个节点上，就意味着您的计算机已经连入Internet网上了。Internet目前的用户已经遍及全球，有超过几亿人在使用Internet，并且它的用户数还在以等比级数上升。

yingyinNormal.en: The Internet's so negative. I try to avoid it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 互联网阴暗负面，我尽量不看呢。

yingyinNormal.en: And I think Internet must find the missing part.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我认为，互联网必须找到那个缺失的部分。

yingyinNormal.en: And also lot of the traditional business hate the Internet, because they destroy their business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而许多传统企业讨厌互联网，因为互联网毁掉了他们的生意。

yingyinNormal.en: But what the rest is that why Internet companies always worry and worry?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是为什么互联网公司总是担忧？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, but we use the Internet to study as well, Mr. Matthews.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，但是我们也用互联网学习啊，马修斯老师。

yingyinNormal.en: Everybody believe that Internet has done great things to the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人都相信互联网为世界做出了伟大的贡献。

yingyinNormal.en: Internet, a part of the century in the past 20 years, was pretty successful, but one thing that is very strange (is) that I found that very few Internet companies can survive peacefully and healthily for more than 3 years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过去20年，互联网非常成功，是我发现一个非常奇怪的事情，很少有互联网公司能健康、平静地活过3年。

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, just one other matter. I want to talk about taxation of Internet commerce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有一件事，我想谈谈互联网商务的税收问题。

yingyinNormal.en: If they look at the Internet, they're gonna think we're pretty ridiculous.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果他们研究互联网的话，他们会觉得我们很可笑。

yingyinNormal.en: But she did dump you. Grow up, Raj. There's no place for truth on the Internet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实是她甩你啊。拉杰，醒醒吧，互联网上无事实。

yingyinNormal.en: But there is the internet and YouTube has proven to be a driving force for world pop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有互联网，油管，已经证明是世界流行音乐的驱动力。

yingyinNormal.en: No, we turned our stereo down by sending a signal around the world via the internet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是，我们通过互联网走了地球一圈发送了一个命令把音响关小的。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, what's going on? Internet's been down for half an hour. Also, Sheldon may be a robot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，过得怎么样？互联网瘫痪半个小时了。还有，谢尔顿可能是机器人。

yingyinNormal.en: Whether we like it or not, in the past 20 years, Internet has launched a huge impact to the human lives.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论你是否喜欢，过去20年，互联网对人类社会产生了巨大的影响。

yingyinNormal.en: That means most of the Internet companies can only have honey days, honey weeks, they don't have even honey months.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这意味着大部分互联网公司只有“蜜日”“蜜周”，他们甚至没有蜜月。

yingyinNormal.en: Alright, Internet is amazing. Before I came here, searching on the Alibaba Internet, the e-commerce site, we found a stamp which is (in)1948, Hannover Messe Export.
yingyinNormal.zh: 互联网很奇妙，在我来这里之前，我在阿里巴巴电子商务网上，我们找到一枚1948年汉诺威梅西出口纪念邮票。

yingyinNormal.en: Olny(Only when) clicks and motors can work together, Internet company can survive, can live happily for next 30 years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有当鼠标和水泥结合时，互联网公司才能活下来，才能开心地活30年。

yingyinNormal.en: Internet purveyors have, for far too long, in my opinion, enjoyed the benefits of no taxation. I find this to be unfair.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我看来，互联网供应商已经享受了太久的无税收福利，我认为这不公平。

yingyinNormal.en: Now what are historians in the future gonna use to help determine who we were? The Internet and my frozen brain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那将来的历史学家会用什么来确定我们现在的样子呢？互联网和我的冷冻的大脑。

yingyinNormal.en: Today I come back again. The reason that I come back again, is trying to find the important missing part of the Internet business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天我又回来了。我回来的原因，是要找到互联网经济缺失的那重要一部分。

examination_example.sentence: A device that combined the functionality of an iPod, phone and <highlight>Internet</highlight> communication into a unit, is navigated by touch.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是一款将iPod、手机和互联网通讯功能结合在一起的设备，通过触摸进行浏览。

examination_example.sentence: A new study argues that all students see a decline in performance when they browse the <highlight>Internet</highlight> during class for non-academic purposes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项新研究认为，所有学生在课堂上浏览非学术网页时，学习表现都会有所下降。

examination_example.sentence: Surfing the <highlight>Internet</highlight> during class doesn't just steal focus from the educator; it also hurts students who're already struggling to grasp the material.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在课堂上网上冲浪不仅会窃取教育者的注意力; 它还伤害了那些已经在努力掌握学习材料的学生。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 所有的网民都称他们为英雄，他们树立了一个好榜样。
